{"tid":278651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本人新西，聽完泰博段錄音感到非常震驚","createTime":"2017-06-10T15:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T07:47:57.000Z","uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4b58dd38d33e563d57b81d5fc4f65ba7e92077","tid":278651,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"講真，一直對熱狗都冇乜好感<br />\n唯獨見到泰博上任後既表現覺得佢唔錯<br />\n原本慎重考慮緊下屆投佢<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本土派仲有乜人係信得過？<br />\n應該話，而家仲有冇木土派呢樣野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92377ade25d0099b0c50b9598e6b194b027f3621","tid":278651,"uid":30807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"你回想下，熱城對本民青既指控根本只係為私利，想獨吞本土派資源<br />\n<br />\n你其實係咪真係咁唔鍾意本民青呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767bfcf055a779fc09396e80e777dff81e5ecf53","tid":278651,"uid":93784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:35:53.000Z","msg":"點會無本土派 <br />\n只係熱狗,國師,青山派 一直都搶本土派話語權, <br />\n靠清算將真正既本土派同港獨派 打成為偽本土,偽港獨 追住黎屌<br />\n其實佢地自己就係偽本土, 偽港獨"},{"pid":"191dce2a4d0c8def0bc6719285d668c086cb55c5","tid":278651,"uid":93784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你回想下，熱城對本民青既指控根本只係為私利，想獨吞本土派資源<br />\n<br />\n你其實係咪真係咁唔鍾意本民青呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個陣班熱狗係撚咁追住本民青黎屌 黎笑<br />\n我都睇唔順眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20868d6e78d6d07e4ed530deca9e372a8005bc24","tid":278651,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"下屆有排"},{"pid":"e0e22d5c916891520e440166fc8f00e27aa647fa","tid":278651,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你回想下，熱城對本民青既指控根本只係為私利，想獨吞本土派資源<br />\n<br />\n你其實係咪真係咁唔鍾意本民青呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我投左黃柒傑，你話呢？<br />\n本民青未成氣候係事實，唔到你駁<br />\n我灰既係連我唯一欣賞既熱狗都係咁既樣<br />\n究竟而家呢班所謂既本土派仲可以點折墮法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58d8a19f52d19a0153cba75d8913f1c6a344fbd","tid":278651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"冷血公民都唔係本土派啦<br />\n<br />\n屌你！"},{"pid":"48fb06770d54488e09d803916631ab9984193fe8","tid":278651,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462025fad267948412ef8beafd3e15eda1555dd4","tid":278651,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"香港只有黃毓民信得過"},{"pid":"52ac72524774ec993a77df36e21246c451df4d67","tid":278651,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下屆有排</blockquote><br />\n我又唔會講死話下屆一定唔撚投佢<br />\n不過呢三年我好難唔用有色眼鏡睇佢<br />\nbtw, 如果陳浩天有得選就好啦"},{"pid":"4e74a0a89a3ae63449b0288190ecb83a5b7faa17","tid":278651,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54fdf0754bb15e0573f7bc68f34cd657171ccd60","tid":278651,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"038b743a9db4115b1dd7bb3981c3150a74f5cc2d","tid":278651,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港只有黃毓民信得過</blockquote><br />\n可惜佢眼光真係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係話埋佢身嘅都只係想上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29f7f6845fd7404c2e8cdd1af3f8f7c0e96a525","tid":278651,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>